OL,4,CPeloton cuts price of bike as sales
OL,5,Cgrowth slows
OL,6, The fitness bike maker Peloton is to
OL,7, slash the price of its flagship bike as
OL,8, people head back to the gym and do less
OL,9, exercise at home.
OL,11,FThe US firm will cut the price of its
OL,12,Fless expensive Bike machine by about
OL,13,F20% to $1,495 (#1,090) from Thursday.
OL,15,FThe change will take effect in all of
OL,16,Fits markets, including the US, UK,
OL,17,FCanada, Australia and Germany.
OL,19,FIt came as losses widened at the firm
OL,20,Fin the fourth quarter of the year and
OL,21,Frevenue growth began to slow.
